<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your OTP for Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .email-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      color: #4CAF50;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #777;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4CAF50;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #4CAF50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Hello, <%= @user.username %>!</h1>

    <h2>We've received a request to verify your account.</h2>

    <p>To complete your verification, please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to confirm your identity:</p>

    <div class="otp-code"><%= @otp %></div>

    <p>Enter this OTP on our platform to proceed with your sign-up and activate your account.</p>

    <a href="[Your Verification URL]" class="cta-button">Complete Verification</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you did not request this verification, please ignore this email. Your account will remain secure.</p>
      <p>If you need assistance, visit our <a href="[Your Support URL]">Help Center</a> or reply to this email.</p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing [Your Platform Name]!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
